episodes.title: Religious Baptism - Bugbrooke  (1975)
episodes.description:
Bugbrooke.



Congregation of men and women young and old holding hands and singing / chanting.  Girl is helped into the water in the centre of the room by two men and another man already in the water claps sings / chants for baptism. Four men in the water (three the same) with arms raised singing. Some of the congregation hug. CU of old woman's face and her hand held up.  Three people smiling link arms and descend into the water together.  Congregation clapping joyfully with eyes closed and singing. The congregation raise their arms and carry on clapping enthusiastically.  
 FILM ID:3370.05
